


\ Just load this file after the RETINA file, like last time. 

\ Note: after using any of the "ify" words, use the "to-mission" command. 
\ Some events take one mission to kick in, so to speak. (Technical hitch.) 

\ Think I'll make these trader camp chars, as to not saturate the road pool. 

